// =============================================
//  components/ — Reusable UI Elements
// =============================================
//  Place shared, presentational React components here.
//  These are small, composable building blocks used
//  across multiple pages.
//
//  Examples:
//    • Button.jsx       → styled button variants
//    • Modal.jsx        → overlay dialog
//    • Navbar.jsx       → top navigation bar
//    • CodeEditor.jsx   → Monaco wrapper component
//
//  Tip: keep components "dumb" — they receive props
//  and render UI, but don't manage global state.
// =============================================
